V0023_01_00_00_0.text: Even before this Duel begins, you already have one foot in the grave!

V0023_01_00_01_1.text: My ghosts are waiting for you to join them!

V0023_01_00_02_0.text:
This is your last chance!
Leave your cards or perish!

V0023_01_00_03_0.text:
Welcome to the Arena of Lost Souls.
Abandon hope. For no one here gets out alive!

V0023_01_00_04_1.text: My ghosts will trap you in a living nightmare, Joey!

V0023_01_00_05_1.text: You're not the boss of me anymore!

V0023_01_00_06_0.text:
Eeeeek!
I have to face your Deck of Terror?!

V0023_01_00_06_1.text:
But since I have no choice...
I'll win this time!

V0023_03_00_04_0.text: This doesn't look good at all...

V0023_05_00_00_0.text: My Ghost Deck will freeze you in fear!

V0023_06_01_02_0.text: Duh! I knew you'd do that!

V0023_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0023_08_00_00_0.text:
Hahaha! Perfect!
Defending won't protect your monster anymore!

V0023_08_00_01_1.text: It'll cost me some Life Points, but I'll gladly pay to get a monster back from the Graveyard!

V0023_08_00_02_0.text: I've got just the card to bury you!

V0023_08_00_02_1.text: The Continuous Trap,  Call of the Haunted!

V0023_08_00_03_1.text: All monsters can't attack for two turns!

V0023_08_00_04_0.text: Now begins my ghost combo! I activate the Continuous Trap, Skull Invitation!

V0023_08_00_06_0.text: Watch as all monsters transform into a horrifying zombie horde!

V0023_08_00_07_0.text: This'll power up my army of zombies!

V0023_08_00_08_0.text: This will put a pep in my zombie's step!

V0023_08_00_09_0.text: Zombies don't stay underground forever! Come on back!

V0023_08_00_10_0.text: I'll begin my zombie combo with this!

V0023_08_00_12_0.text: Here's my Quick-Play Spell, Burial from a Different Dimension!

V0023_08_00_12_1.text: Banished monsters return to my Graveyard!

V0023_08_00_13_1.text: I bury a monster from the Deck into the graveyard!

V0023_08_00_14_1.text: I discard a card from my hand to return a monster from my Graveyard!

V0023_09_00_00_0.text: Pumpking the King of Ghosts' effect activates! Ectoplasmic Fortification!

V0023_09_00_02_0.text: Pumprincess the Princess of Ghosts' effect activates!

V0023_09_00_05_0.text: King of the Skull Servants' effect activates!

V0023_09_00_09_0.text: Castle of Dark Illusions' effect activates!

V0023_10_00_02_0.text: Don't get TOO scared by this!

V0023_11_00_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Attack Position!

V0023_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0023_13_00_00_0.text:
Mwahahaha!
Here comes the leader of all my ghosts!

V0023_13_00_07_0.text: I'm digging up The The Snake Hair!

V0023_13_00_08_0.text: This'll send shivers down your spine! Behold! Great Mammoth of Goldfine!

V0023_13_00_10_0.text: This ghost is perfect! Pumprincess the Princess of Ghosts!

V0023_13_00_11_0.text: I'll play this ghost! The Wandering Doomed!

V0023_13_00_13_0.text: Stumbling in are my Three-Legged Zombies!

V0023_13_00_14_0.text: You won't win a staring contest against this guy!

V0023_13_00_18_0.text: Witness my ghost card! Skull Servant!

V0023_13_00_19_0.text: I play my ghost card! King of the Skull Servants!

V0023_13_00_20_0.text: My ghost can't wait to meet you! The Lady in Wight!

V0023_13_00_21_0.text: This'll make you believe in ghosts! Wightprince!

V0023_13_00_23_0.text: This ghost card will work! Wightmare!

V0023_13_00_24_0.text: I'll power up Pumpking the King of Ghosts with this! Castle of Dark Illusions!

V0023_13_00_25_0.text: Humph. This Warrior's nothing special. Bleh.

V0023_15_00_00_0.text: There's no way to escape from your fear!

V0023_19_00_00_0.text: Attack, Pumpking the King of Ghosts!

V0023_19_00_01_0.text: Wipe the floor with 'em,  Crass Clown!

V0023_19_00_08_0.text: Great Mammoth of Goldfine of Goldfine! Trample 'em!

V0023_19_00_10_0.text: Spook 'em, Pumprincess the Princess of Ghosts!

V0023_19_00_19_0.text: King of the Skull Servants! Show 'em why you're king!

V0023_19_00_24_0.text: Castle of Dark Illusions! Float and attack!

V0023_21_00_00_0.text:
I end my turn!
You'll be resting in peace in no time!

V0023_21_00_02_0.text:
Not good... Definitely not good...
I end my turn...

V0023_28_00_00_1.text: You didn't stand a ghost of a chance!

V0023_28_00_02_1.text: There's no strategy that can defeat me! Not in this world - nor the next!

V0023_28_00_03_0.text:
Hahahaha!
Make no Bonz about it - I'm the greatest Duelist there is!

V0023_28_00_03_1.text: I'll never lose to you, dweeb!

V0023_28_00_04_1.text: Even a coward will call you a coward!

V0023_28_00_05_1.text: Maybe it's time that YOU start calling ME your boss!

V0023_28_00_06_0.text: You call that a Deck of Terror?

V0023_28_00_06_1.text: My ghosts were much more terrifying!

V0023_29_00_03_0.text:
Wait, wut? How? What?
What just happened?!?

V0023_30_00_00_0.text: You can't hide the truth - you're definitely spooked by my ghosts!

V0023_30_00_01_0.text: Come on! Play your next card!

V0023_30_00_02_0.text: Can you be any more of a scaredy-cat?

V0023_33_00_00_0.text: The ghosts of the past are all around you!

V0023_33_00_02_0.text: This arena will be your graveyard!

V0023_34_00_01_0.text: Want me to play a card, or would you rather defeat yourself?

V0023_34_00_03_0.text: If you leave me your cards, maybe I won't snuff you out.

V0023_34_00_05_0.text: I'll spook you into submission with my ghost cards!

V0023_34_00_07_0.text:
Hee hee hee!
My zombies will swarm all over you!

V0023_35_00_00_0.text: Leave it to Bonz to haunt your nightmares!

V0023_35_00_01_0.text: Time to give up the ghost!

V0023_36_00_00_0.text:
Yeah! Excellent!
Our tag team is perfection itself!

V0023_36_00_02_0.text: I hope you know what to do...

V0023_36_00_03_0.text:
Hahahaha!
I bet I can even win this on my own!

V0023_36_00_05_0.text: T-This is all your fault! So clean up your mess!

V0023_36_00_06_0.text:
Hahahaha!
Together, our living dead will fill them with living dread!

V0023_36_00_08_0.text: I couldn't scare 'em into submission - I hope you can!
